00:40:13,622 --> 00:40:15,164
All right.

294
00:40:17,039 --> 00:40:19,331
You do understand.

295
00:40:19,414 --> 00:40:21,914
I want to hear...
I want to hear you talk.

296
00:40:22,039 --> 00:40:24,831
We're gonna show them that
you're not a wall. Understand?

297
00:40:24,914 --> 00:40:27,664
I want you to talk to me.

298
00:40:27,747 --> 00:40:31,706
All right, now,
I want to hear you say it.

299
00:40:31,789 --> 00:40:34,289
I've got to hear how
you say things.

300
00:40:34,414 --> 00:40:38,789
I won't hurt you. I've got to hear
and understand how you say things.

301
00:40:38,914 --> 00:40:42,289
Very slowly,
