302
00:40:44,414 --> 00:40:45,664
Say, "Yes."

303
00:40:50,997 --> 00:40:52,872
Yes.

304
00:40:53,956 --> 00:40:55,414
Yes!

305
00:40:55,539 --> 00:40:56,956
Good.

306
00:40:57,706 --> 00:41:01,081
All right, now, just once more
