"John Merrick."

317
00:41:38,414 --> 00:41:41,622
No. John... That's very good.

318
00:41:41,747 --> 00:41:43,914
Say, "John Merrick."

319
00:41:48,414 --> 00:41:52,539
"Hello. My name is John Merrick."

320
00:41:54,706 --> 00:41:55,956
Hello.

321
00:41:56,081 --> 00:41:59,414
My name is...

322
00:41:59,497 --> 00:42:02,081
John Merrick.

323
00:42:02,206 --> 00:42:03,539
You can speak.

324
00:42:12,206 --> 00:42:14,206
How did you get up here?

325
00:42:15,706 --> 00:42:17,622
I want my man back.

326
00:42:17,747 --> 00:42:22,331
