329
00:42:26,914 --> 00:42:28,539
Don't!

330
00:42:29,914 --> 00:42:31,997
Don't.

331
00:42:32,081 --> 00:42:36,081
You've had plenty of time to...

332
00:42:36,206 --> 00:42:38,331
cure him.

333
00:42:38,414 --> 00:42:41,081
And now he's leaving with me.

334
00:42:41,206 --> 00:42:46,414
Do you understand me now,
Mr. Treves?

335
