from another man's misery.

342
00:43:05,414 --> 00:43:07,372
Do you think
you're better than me?

343
00:43:07,456 --> 00:43:09,372
No, I never said that.

344
00:43:09,456 --> 00:43:13,039
You wanted the freak...

345
00:43:13,122 --> 00:43:16,581
to show to those doctor chums of
yours, to make a name for yourself.

346
00:43:16,664 --> 00:43:18,622
You, my friend.

347
00:43:20,206 --> 00:43:25,247
I gave you the freak on trust...

348
00:43:25,372 --> 00:43:28,414
in the name of science...

349
00:43:28,497 --> 00:43:30,456
and now I want him back!

350
00:43:30,581 --> 00:43:32,581
You do not own this man!
Now stop it!

351
00:43:33,497 --> 00:43:35,247
I want him back!

352
