375
00:45:24,622 --> 00:45:27,997
Righteousness. Righteousness.

376
00:45:29,664 --> 00:45:34,247
He leadeth me in the paths
of righteousness...

377
00:45:34,331 --> 00:45:36,831
for His name's sake.

378
00:45:36,914 --> 00:45:39,956
Good. That's very good. Good.

379
00:45:40,081 --> 00:45:44,372
When your visitor comes today, say
it exactly the way you've said it.

380
00:45:44,456 --> 00:45:49,164
So when I introduce him to you,
say the words that you've learned.

381
00:45:49,247 --> 00:45:52,997
If you have trouble with any words,
I'll help you, so don't worry.

382
00:45:53,081 --> 00:45:55,581
I will introduce him to you
and say...

383
00:45:55,664 --> 00:45:58,039
"Please meet Mr. Carr Gomm."

384
00:45:58,122 --> 00:45:59,706
And you will say?

385
00:46:00,914 --> 00:46:05,497
Hello. My name is John Merrick.

386
00:46:05,581 --> 00:46:07,831
I'm very pleased to meet you.

387
00:46:09,122 --> 00:46:11,581
Good! Good.

388
00:46:11,706 --> 00:46:14,622
I'll go and get Mr. Carr Gomm.

389
00:46:20,247 --> 00:46:22,872
It is only a physical problem.

390
00:46:24,539 --> 00:46:27,247
He has trouble with certain sounds
because of...

391
00:46:27,372 --> 00:46:30,664
the constrictive deformity
of the mouth, but he can talk.

392
00:46:30,747 --> 00:46:34,581
Talking's one thing, but is he able
to understand what's said to him?

393
00:46:34,664 --> 00:46:37,622
Yes. Oh, yes! Except...

394
00:46:37,747 --> 00:46:41,706
Except he's so anxious to make
a good impression on you...

395
00:46:41,789 --> 00:46:43,997
that he might seem a little nervous.

396
00:47:01,831 --> 00:47:03,289
Come in.

397
00:47:17,456 --> 00:47:18,664
John...

398
00:47:18,747 --> 00:47:21,831
may I introduce you
to Mr. Carr Gomm?

399
00:47:21,914 --> 00:47:24,956
Mr. Carr Gomm,
this is John Merrick.

400
00:47:26,039 --> 00:47:29,581
Hello. My name is John Merrick.

401
00:47:29,664 --> 00:47:31,622
I'm very pleased to meet you.

402
00:47:31,747 --> 00:47:33,831
I'm very pleased to meet you.

403
00:47:36,456 --> 00:47:38,372
How are you feeling today?

404
00:47:38,456 --> 00:47:41,122
I feel much better.

405
00:47:42,581 --> 00:47:44,706
Are you comfortable here?

406
00:47:47,372 --> 00:47:50,456
Everybody's been very kind.

407
00:47:51,414 --> 00:47:53,372
How is your bronchitis?

408
00:48:05,581 --> 00:48:08,081
Mr. Merrick likes the food here,
don't you?

409
00:48:12,706 --> 00:48:16,206
Much better than what
