419
00:48:55,456 --> 00:48:59,789
How long did you and Mr. Treves
prepare for this interview?

420
00:49:06,581 --> 00:49:10,581
Everybody's been very kind.

421
00:49:10,706 --> 00:49:12,581
Yes, of course, I understand.

422
00:49:12,706 --> 00:49:15,622
Well, it's been a pleasure
meeting you, Mr. Merrick.

423
00:49:15,747 --> 00:49:17,872
Good day to you.

424
00:49:27,581 --> 00:49:29,456
Very good, John.

425
00:49:29,581 --> 00:49:31,456
It was very good.

426
00:49:31,581 --> 00:49:33,456
I'll be back in a moment.

427
00:49:37,581 --> 00:49:40,414
The Lord is my shepherd...

428
00:49:41,456 --> 00:49:43,789
I shall not want.

429
00:49:44,872 --> 00:49:46,747
He maketh me lie down...

