435
00:50:03,622 --> 00:50:06,581
I'm sorry things have turned out
this way. Good day to you.

436
00:50:06,664 --> 00:50:08,081
Yea...

437
00:50:09,414 --> 00:50:12,914
though I walk through the valley
of the shadow of death...

438
00:50:13,039 --> 00:50:14,831
I fear no evil...

439
00:50:14,914 --> 00:50:17,747
