The 23rd Psalm.

452
00:51:05,039 --> 00:51:09,706
I used to read the Bible every day.

453
00:51:11,456 --> 00:51:14,081
I know it very well...

454
00:51:14,164 --> 00:51:16,456
and the Book of Common Prayer.

455
00:51:17,997 --> 00:51:21,914
The 23rd Psalm is very beautiful.
It's my favorite.

456
00:51:24,747 --> 00:51:27,872
Treves, come and see me in my office
when you're through up here.

457
00:51:27,956 --> 00:51:29,914
There's something important
I want to say to you.

458
00:51:31,247 --> 00:51:34,956
Good-bye, Mr. Merrick.
