Good night, and sleep well.

1016
01:54:45,539 --> 01:54:49,289
- And you too, my friend.
- Yes.

1017
01:54:49,414 --> 01:54:51,831
I'm so pleased
you enjoyed yourself.

1018
01:54:51,914 --> 01:54:54,039
Good night.

1019
01:54:57,497 --> 01:54:59,081
Good night.

1020
